Description: The young wizard Negi Springfield meets a sinister fellow who claims he can solve some mysteries, but at what price?
Title: NEGIMA! 28
Author: Ken Akamatsu

Description: Poor Naruto: he must cope with a ninja summit and a target on the back of his good friend, Sasuke.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 49
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 3
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: Maka, an arms expert, wants to turn the Soul Eater, her living scythe, into the ultimate weapon for Death.
Title: SOUL EATER, VOL. 4
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Troubled by spirits that only he can see, Watanuki Kimiharo strikes a Faustian bargain with an alluring witch to get rid of them.
Title: XXXHOLIC, VOL. 16
Author: Clamp

Description: Oz has finally escaped the prison known as the Abyss, but his life does not seem much better.
Title: PANDORA HEARTS, VOL. 3
Author: Jun Mochizuki

Description: From the publisher: "Get ready to brush up on world history with these handsome and hysterical personifications of the Axis Powers as they meet, become friends and form one of the most powerful alliances the world has ever seen."
Title: HETALIA AXIS POWERS, VOL. 1
Author: Hidekaz Himaruya

Description: This is not your typical night school. The student body at this one includes werewolves, vampires and witches. The curriculum? Spelling and spell-casting.
Title: NIGHTSCHOOL, VOL. 4
Author: Svetlana Chmakova

Description: Misao Harada can see into a magical realm where she is the bride demon of prophecy. How will she survive the pursuit of demons who want the power in her blood?
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 6
Author: Kanoko Sakurakoji

Description: The SOS Brigade, a school club dedicated to meeting time travelers or aliens or anyone fantastic, faces off against the Computer Research Society. At stake: the fate of the city!
Title: THE MELANCHOLY OF HARUHI SUZUMIYA, VOL. 7
Author: Nagaru Tanigawa and Gaku Tsugano
Contributor: by Nagaru Tanigawa and Gaku Tsugano
